===[[Season 4]]===
[[File:Daemon spear.png|thumb|left|250px|Daemon squiring for Prince Oberyn.]]
Ser Daemon squires for Prince [[Oberyn Martell]] during [[Tyrion Lannister]]'s [[Second Trial by Combat of Tyrion Lannister|trial by combat]], and coats his master's spear head with deadly [[Manticores|manticore]] [[Poison|venom]]. He witnesses the Red Viper's death at the hands of Ser [[Gregor Clegane]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Mountain and the Viper]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
